{"h9c63ad2ag0d6eg4481g99b0ge3bde7eeab36": ["*Lae'zel's bemused eyes are fixed on your face.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "21c3040c-1ee1-420a-a2c1-974583bde489"], "h5b405f17g5f98g4dc3g89d1g85e5a53018ae": ["What in the Hells' deepest pits were you <i>thinking?</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "a83a8576-0d8b-43b6-9e2f-4df39b57da5a"], "hb596520dg32fag4d16g8458g51fef99d2cb6": ["What do you mean?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "760b8816-d431-8395-062c-c09252898cb9"], "hd5156fc3g8e46g4edeg8437g5c7568fd12c5": ["I lead you down the one path to purification. Yet you sacrifice your eye to one charlatan, and invite another to mock you for it.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "2cd05d0d-1760-dae0-1266-4788d4c968f6"], "h13a95d7cg138fg4492g83afg9078fb7331df": ["I can't decide whether you're excessively trustful or simply stupid.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "b8677ef8-23ef-d02b-d67b-2749f4cf9af9"], "h50a4544cgd148g45a6ga702g4185a0e6fa2d": ["Or whether there is a difference worth discerning.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "5fa254f2-f1f2-b316-5b79-383db03cd346"], "h44dbac6ag1f4eg4240g988eg59e61b1c7d7b": ["Vlaakith might exile you from the Empire, if she witnessed such naivete.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "a62ba2b2-6831-30c3-2a1c-4c8e82b70235"], "he0c99f0bgbf5ag4f25g91f9g06bf3fd8c18c": ["I don't appreciate your scorn.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "6a9f2c77-1748-9e96-6853-8aa89e325898"], "h728c4a6bgb91eg4a1bg9705g82cc1b8c9f63": ["And I do not appreciate your ignorance, yet apparently I must learn to accept it.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "c1a10d20-ba76-f21e-029f-47f47cfffc82"], "hf5220de4g9b51g459cga322g640cfa1213b0": ["It was a regrettable decision.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "b2d77946-2b87-eb81-a4dd-0e5f1cb0e92b"], "he0844579g271ag4691g956eg0068c37c2b02": ["Such is my grace that I will not speak more of it.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "a8c9e82d-6928-cf8e-b255-d2c5c44c550f"], "h0fe6c6d0g33d6g40f7g9886g4925e61bb87e": ["Desperate times require desperate measures.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "d38e15c2-119d-dcec-5a32-edc267a98ed1"], "hbfe10525g6fd1g459dgb30bg56073efb6d41": ["<i>My Queen's protocol has already provided the measures.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "9c7658bf-206a-bea1-5c46-f41bbc84488b"], "h2d92f093g4b6fg4ba0g9022gcf4536168056": ["You need to back off. Now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "199a4b9e-ad5d-8836-cc42-1f2f71ccb1a5"], "h2a1277c2g17aag4d8bg8d30g3751a72e4a8e": ["<i>Chk</i>. Such is my grace that I will not speak more of it.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "b7aacc04-f7cb-3e0f-c57a-12150432c966"], "he65d2460g1860g4e9dg8de4g542dac723a26": ["Vlaakith would be <i>proud </i>I've gone to such lengths for purification.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "ddcf4a4b-a488-7834-9283-ba94aff1b9cc"], "h65c6a491gba7cg4142g9080gc1aafcc17751": ["<i>Vlaakith has already provided the means.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "7d5b9cd9-03fd-5c34-18ae-0ee28f781824"], "h22a07adfg33ceg49b4g91aeg589fe8362910": ["<i>Bah. </i>Let us speak no more of it, lest I lash out with more than my tongue.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "ac2683a9-3571-b035-a4ea-029926002a66"], "h0c34f553g548ag420eg89cbg97cf4a70b011": ["<i>Bow your head in deference to her wisdom.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "a0214d8c-89c3-067b-3698-cb97ff6cc738"], "h52e0c19dg1ca7g4e3dgaff3gb56ffc776cda": ["Such is my grace that I would not carry word to her.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "38fb4594-05c8-d624-d144-b5c11ffee317"], "h98330d38g3eebg44f2gaa98g580d864e185e": ["Such is my disdain that I will not forget.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "fa908a76-f620-afea-4407-3ea86a6177e5"], "h7d45ef42g09b3g4bfcg8af7gc621615b7b48": ["I was sure Volo could help us.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "4bb69dee-fb67-c2c1-a933-edad029cd51f"], "ha4d24641g2d31g46ebg9bcdg81bcda7ef0c2": ["I had to try <i>something</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "b5c8e09f-3a8a-871a-f6cf-ada1aec1730c"], "hdaf8b85eg8151g4e2ag9864gb2706fd14b23": ["Volo is clearly learned. Perhaps his technique was lacking.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "1780cd48-1c86-df2e-9e8e-fc8c2e84293d"], "hb1272594gecbbg4605gbf74ge3fd6ccef10b": ["You think this a problem of <i>technique?</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "9ac046a6-c38e-e023-6d7e-c99bc8726e2c"], "hc6e799eeg30cfg49f5gb151gc5db70a8de22": ["I should have been wary. The tool was archaic, and his grip was appalling.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "2ecd8f2b-b933-1ee1-5b78-59e7e0c71d62"], "h7b1e267cgf6a5g4a72ga2c7g500fccbc02ef": ["Charlatans. Half-blinded halfwits. I am beset on all sides.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "00aa6b53-26e3-95a0-a6ee-ba0e2bbcf16c"], "hf662744fg6caag4745gb6efg6ca5e2920171": ["Bah. Let us not speak of it, lest I lash out with more than my tongue.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostVolo_CRD_Laezel.html", "76e64c72-421a-299e-709a-bdc950989265"]}